properties.NAME: Bernhard Road
properties.JUST: Recent traffic signal at Bernhard and SR 85 has increased traffic on Bernhard.  This segment is part of larger alignment that provides east-west connectivity between Peachtree City, SR 85 and SR 92.

properties.NAME: Antioch Road
properties.DESC: Two-lane road, shoulder and ditch, feeds traffic to and from State Routes and City of Fayetteville.
properties.JUST: Antioch is classified as Major Collector north and south of this segment.

properties.NAME: Goza Road
properties.JUST: Provides east-west connectivity between SR 85 and SR 92.  Proposed change is consistent with adjacent Bernhard Road and a better fit with East Fayetteville Bypass to the east.

properties.NAME: Corinth Road
properties.DESC: Two-lane road, shoulder & ditch, recent traffic signal installation at SR 54.
properties.JUST: Road receives heavy traffic between SR 85 and SR 54.  Recommend consistent classification from SR 54 to 855 (i.e., through Clayton County segment)
